data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Recently remodeled three-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch. Revel in the beauty of refinished wood floors as you enter with a flood of natural light coming from the living room picture window. Other awesome features include a large eat-in kitchen with all appliances included, updated full bathroom showcasing exquisite tile work, and a spacious primary bedroom with double closets and an attached bathroom. Updated Anderson windows help save on utility costs, and updated electrical panel offers peace of mind. Outside, a great backyard space with a privacy fence, covered patio, and large wood deck offers ample space for entertaining and gardening. Come see it today!
